                            Hi hades=2C<br>
<br>
Thanks for connecting with us at Topcoder. We=E2=80=99re excited to chat w=
ith you and we=E2=80=99ll be in touch very soon to set up a call.<br>
<br>
It=E2=80=99s important for you to know that organizations and individuals=
 engage Topcoder in 2 distinct ways:<br>
<br>
1) Self-Service through our web application Topcoder Connect to do design=
 and development of solutions and apps<br>
<br>
Here's a quick video to see how this self-service application will work fo=
r you:<br>
<br>
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3DEdbdJIcqb6A<br>
<br>
2) Many customers use their existing Global Systems Integrator (GSI) or cr=
owdsourcing consultants we have actively partnered with who are experts in=
 crowdsourcing delivery. <em><strong>Topcoder is partnered with 7 out of t=
he top 10 GSI's and we have several=2C smaller consultancies who service o=
